{"TopicId":143175,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[KSP 1.3.1] Keep It Straight - Camera Persistent Mode (1.0.3 - 2017-10-11)","CreatedByName":"RealGecko","CreatedById":162682,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-05T22:11:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"RealGecko","CreatedById":162682,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-05T22:11:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen I\u0027m on a low orbit I prefer FREE camera mode, cause body I\u0027m \u0022falling to\u0022 has to be \u0022below\u0022 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever KSP keeps switching camera mode to AUTO every time something happens: switched to far away vessel, ended docking etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo here is Keep It Straight - mod that saves camera mode between scene changes and restores it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EPhotorealistic pictures from high orbit:\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022l2TvNlv.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://imgur.com/l2TvNlv.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022LKynjPl.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://imgur.com/LKynjPl.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo more, no less \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://spacedock.info/mod/824/Keep%20It%20Straight\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESpace Dock\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/Real-Gecko/KSP-KeepItStraight\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESource\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/Real-Gecko/KSP-KeepItStraight/blob/master/LICENSE.md\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EGPLv3 License\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EChangelog:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVersion 1.0.3\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nRecompile for KSP 1.3.1\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nVersion 1.0.2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nRecompile for KSP 1.3.0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nVersion 1.0.1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nCamera mode is not reset to AUTO after docking is complete\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-10-11T07:49:40Z\u0022 title=\u002210/11/2017 07:49  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 11, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by RealGecko\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EJAMU\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deimos Rast","CreatedById":157420,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-05T22:35:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNeeds to be stock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nedit\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nfyi spacedoc link says \u0022unauthorized\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-05T22:36:38Z\u0022 title=\u002207/05/2016 10:36  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 5, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Deimos Rast\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealGecko","CreatedById":162682,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-05T22:42:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222662754\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467758154\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157420\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deimos Rast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, Deimos Rast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNeeds to be stock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDefinitely!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222662754\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467758154\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157420\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deimos Rast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, Deimos Rast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nfyi spacedoc link says \u0022unauthorized\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI bet mod is not \u0022published\u0022 by admins yet, that\u0027s why it is not showed in \u003Cspan\u003E\u0022\u003C/span\u003Enew mods\u0022 section and not accessible to others.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGrab it from \u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/Real-Gecko/KSP-KeepItStraight/releases/download/1.0.0/KeepItStraight-1.0.0.zip\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehere\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"White Owl","CreatedById":10849,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-06T00:27:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you, thank you, thank you, thank you! I freaking \u003Cem\u003Ehate\u003C/em\u003E the default camera behavior, and the old mod that made free mode the new default doesn\u0027t work anymore. This is perfect.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-06T01:23:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222662754\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467758154\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157420\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deimos Rast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Deimos Rast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nfyi spacedoc link says \u0022unauthorized\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222662759\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467758539\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022162682\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealGecko\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, RealGecko said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI bet mod is not \u0022published\u0022 by admins yet, that\u0027s why it is not showed in \u003Cspan\u003E\u0022\u003C/span\u003Enew mods\u0022 section and not accessible to others.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nActually, you are \u0022half\u0022 correct... Its not published yet... But it\u0027s YOU who has to hit the \u0022Publish Mod\u0022 button on SpaceDock...Once YOU hit that button, mods are pretty much IMMEDIATELY available on SpaceDock... Unlike Curse, or others, which seem to take up to a whole day or more to \u0022publish\u0022\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSeems this is an easy thing to miss, which LOTS of people seem to do... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealGecko","CreatedById":162682,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-06T08:39:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222662928\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467768198\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut it\u0027s YOU who has to hit the \u0022Publish Mod\u0022 button on SpaceDock...\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh man, tis was 4 AM, my brain refused to work \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"politas","CreatedById":119649,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-20T11:09:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdded to \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E, per request.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deimos Rast","CreatedById":157420,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-24T23:03:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ngrats on getting featured on spacedock!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, the forum thread link links to a comment in the middle of the thread, not the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geschosskopf","CreatedById":69507,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-24T23:57:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222662727\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467756662\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022162682\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealGecko\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/5/2016 at 5:11 PM, RealGecko said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo here is Keep It Straight - mod that saves camera mode between scene changes and restores it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave a virtual keg! \u00A0This is a consummation that long has been devoutly wished.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealGecko","CreatedById":162682,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-25T04:34:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222689684\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221469401398\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157420\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deimos Rast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Deimos Rast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, the forum thread link links to a comment in the middle of the thread, not the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFixed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dambuster6178","CreatedById":166632,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-12T09:45:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi this looks good but where do i put the file too thanks\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nChris\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:lol:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_laugh.png\u0022 title=\u0022:lol:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealGecko","CreatedById":162682,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-12T20:53:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222714296\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470995126\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166632\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022dambuster6178\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, dambuster6178 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi this looks good but where do i put the file too thanks\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi there, unpack archive to you KSP installation\u0027s GameData. Or even better recipe: use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealGecko","CreatedById":162682,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-12T20:21:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVersion \u003Cstrong\u003E1.0.1\u003C/strong\u003E is out:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Camera mode is not reset to AUTO after docking is complete\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP 1.2 compatible\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Errol","CreatedById":118622,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-12T18:16:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162682-realgecko/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022162682\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162682-realgecko/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@RealGecko\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0I noticed that the version you have up on spacedock is listed as compatible with 1.2.2, but the included version file lists the max ksp version as 1.2.0.......just a heads up so you can update that if you have time.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealGecko","CreatedById":162682,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-13T05:01:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222952916\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221486923413\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022118622\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Errol\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 13.02.2017 at 0:16 AM, Errol said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162682-realgecko/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022162682\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162682-realgecko/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@RealGecko\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0I noticed that the version you have up on spacedock is listed as compatible with 1.2.2, but the included version file lists the max ksp version as 1.2.0.......just a heads up so you can update that if you have time.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep, did not update \u003Cem\u003E.version \u003C/em\u003Efile for a while. Nothing to worry about unless you use AVC.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealGecko","CreatedById":162682,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-30T09:32:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVersion 1.0.2 for KSP 1.3.0 is here. No functionality changes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-28T15:51:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162682-realgecko/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022162682\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162682-realgecko/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@RealGecko\u003C/a\u003E Just what I was looking for.\u00A0 Does it/Can it work with Improved Chase Cam?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jacke","CreatedById":103694,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-21T15:49:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was wondering if \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/141180-13-easy-vessel-switch-evs-v130/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EEasy Vessel Switch\u003C/a\u003E and \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/143175-ksp-130-keep-it-straight-camera-persistent-mode-102-2017-05-30/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EKeep It Straight\u003C/a\u003E would interfere with one another, as what they do is similar.\u00A0 (Posted in both topics.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-08-21T15:49:35Z\u0022 title=\u002208/21/2017 03:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 21, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Jacke\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jacke","CreatedById":103694,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-21T21:58:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThe reply in the Easy Vessel Switch topic from \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/155445-igorz/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022155445\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/155445-igorz/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@IgorZ\u003C/a\u003E.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223154006\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022141180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221503337301\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155445\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022IgorZ\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, IgorZ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEVS doesn\u0027t change the camera mode, it only deals with the camera position and orientation. So I\u0027d\u00A0say there should be no issues.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealGecko","CreatedById":162682,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-11T07:50:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpdate 1.0.3 for KSP 1.3.1, no functionality changes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-07T16:29:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew version of KSP is up, but I\u0027ll probably wait for version 1.4.1 next week to update this and create a new thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jiraiyah","CreatedById":97667,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-11T20:11:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223312742\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520440144\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022168379\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022maja\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/7/2018 at 4:29 PM, maja said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew version of KSP is up, but I\u0027ll probably wait for version 1.4.1 next week to update this and create a new thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis it a normal process for ksp to have a patch in one week?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-11T20:13:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223317298\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520799065\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002297667\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jiraiyah\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Jiraiyah said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis it a normal process for ksp to have a patch in one week?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, but this was announced.\u00A0 One reason is to fix any immediate, obvious bugs, the other is for the Making History DLC\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-14T09:06:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EPromised update for KSP 1.4.1 and a new thread are here:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1819700785\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/172244-ksp-141-keep-it-straight-camera-persistent-mode-104-2018-03-14/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:212px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u00